    	</description>
        <env-entry-name>wl.analytics.url</env-entry-name>
        <env-entry-type>java.lang.String</env-entry-type>
        <env-entry-value/>
    </env-entry>
    
    <env-entry>
    	<description>[OPTIONAL] The basic authorized user name for the URL entered in wl.analytics.url.</description>
